OL,4,CPremier League: Richard Masters reveals
OL,5,Cplans to tackle racism in football
OL,6, The Premier League's acting chief
OL,7, executive says "one instance of racism
OL,8, is too many" as he laid out plans to
OL,9, tackle the issue in the game.
OL,11,FRichard Masters says measures are being
OL,12,Fput in place to improve stewarding and
OL,13,Fmake it easier for fans to report
OL,14,Finstances of racism.
OL,16,FLast season saw a number of racist
OL,17,Fincidents involving high-profile
OL,18,Fplayers such as Raheem Sterling.
OL,20,F"We're determined to tackle
OL,21,Fdiscrimination," said Masters.
